{"id":26726,"date":"2024-02-25T02:49:53","date_gmt":"2021-10-24T21:19:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=26726"},"modified":"2022-08-30T14:26:23","modified_gmt":"2022-08-30T08:56:23","slug":"glass-wall-bedroom","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/glass-wall-bedroom\/","title":{"rendered":"6 Sleek Glass Wall Bedroom Design For Your Stylish Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Some elegant glass wall designs for your bedroom to help you enjoy a natural panoramic view from the comfort of your bed<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The bedroom is one of the most comfortable zones of your home. It is the space where you can cut off from the entire world and create a vibe of your own. Therefore, your focus should be to design a bedroom that brings maximum relaxation and calming ambience to your home and life. If you live in a penthouse, a skyscraper with a mesmerising panoramic view of nature, or cramped up in a small studio apartment, these glass wall designs will add dimensions to your bedroom decor, making it look stylish and comforting. Read along to know more about glass wall bedroom designs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Glass Wall Master Bedroom With An Astonishing View<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are lucky to have a mesmerising view from your bedroom, why hide it with a concrete wall? Go for a glass wall and enjoy the scenic beauty of nature from the comfort of your bed. You can also use a glass folding door in case your bedroom leads to a balcony. Stick to a minimalistic decor and let the natural view from your glass door be the focal point of your bedroom. Add a textured wallpaper on your accent wall, some pendant lights, solid wood furniture and you are good to go.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023136\/1glass-wall-bedroom-with-an-astonishing-view.jpg\" alt=\"Glass wall bedroom with an astonishing view to bring in a splash of nature to your home interiors\" data-id=\"26727\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023136\/1glass-wall-bedroom-with-an-astonishing-view.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=26727\" class=\"wp-image-26727\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023136\/1glass-wall-bedroom-with-an-astonishing-view.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023136\/1glass-wall-bedroom-with-an-astonishing-view-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023136\/1glass-wall-bedroom-with-an-astonishing-view-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023136\/1glass-wall-bedroom-with-an-astonishing-view-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Intelligently Designed Glass Wall Separating Kitchen And The Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Studio apartments with attached kitchens are very functional but can feel a little cramped up. If you are looking for innovative ideas to create a subtle demarcation without making it look too heavy for the eye, we suggest you opt for a glass wall separating the kitchen from your bedroom. It will help you avoid all the kitchen smoke from letting in your bedroom while flaunting your modular kitchen to your guest.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023434\/intelligently-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-aeparating-kitchen-and-the-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Intelligently glass wall design for bedroom aeparating kitchen and the bedroom with wall separating the kitchen and bedroom\" data-id=\"26728\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023434\/intelligently-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-aeparating-kitchen-and-the-bedroom.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=26728\" class=\"wp-image-26728\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023434\/intelligently-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-aeparating-kitchen-and-the-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023434\/intelligently-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-aeparating-kitchen-and-the-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023434\/intelligently-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-aeparating-kitchen-and-the-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023434\/intelligently-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-aeparating-kitchen-and-the-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Glass Wall Between Bathroom And Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A glass wall to separate your bathroom from the bedroom is a smart way of creating a partition while making your contemporary home look spacious and airy. If this design seems too bold for you, opt for a tinted glass, etched glass wall or simply design your glass walls with some shower curtains or blinds. Pull it down while taking a shower, and for the rest of the day, just enjoy the vibrance the glass wall creates in your bedroom. Opt for marble flooring or vitrified tiles, keep your walls muted or white and use spotlights on the ceiling. Glass reflects light beautifully, making your room look bright and spacious. You can also add some pops of colour through pillows and bedsheets to offset the monotony of white.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023718\/master-bedroom-glass-wall-between-bathroom-and-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Master bedroom glass wall between bathroom and bedroom separating the bedroom from the shower area\" data-id=\"26729\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023718\/master-bedroom-glass-wall-between-bathroom-and-bedroom.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=26729\" class=\"wp-image-26729\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023718\/master-bedroom-glass-wall-between-bathroom-and-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023718\/master-bedroom-glass-wall-between-bathroom-and-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023718\/master-bedroom-glass-wall-between-bathroom-and-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023718\/master-bedroom-glass-wall-between-bathroom-and-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Contemporary-style home interiors with a glass partition wall separating the bedroom from the shower area<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Glass Partition Wall For Bedroom And Home Office<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With this current pandemic situation, having your own work-from-home set-up has become more of a necessity than a luxury because working from your bed can take a toll on your productivity and physical health. Setting up a home office can be a little difficult if you live in a small apartment. So we have got you a brilliant idea to create a cosy office space within your bedroom. This office space is ergonomic, efficient and houses all your office essentials. The glass partition creates a subtle office vibe within your bedroom without making the interiors look stuffed.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023935\/glass-wall-bedroom-partition-wall-for-bedroom-and-home-office.jpg\" alt=\"Glass wall bedroom partition wall for bedroom and home office where you get your work done with ease\" data-id=\"26730\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023935\/glass-wall-bedroom-partition-wall-for-bedroom-and-home-office.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=26730\" class=\"wp-image-26730\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023935\/glass-wall-bedroom-partition-wall-for-bedroom-and-home-office.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023935\/glass-wall-bedroom-partition-wall-for-bedroom-and-home-office-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023935\/glass-wall-bedroom-partition-wall-for-bedroom-and-home-office-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25023935\/glass-wall-bedroom-partition-wall-for-bedroom-and-home-office-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">A perfect home office space within your bedroom where you can concentrate and get your work done with ease<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Sliding Glass Wall For Bedroom And Walk-In Closet<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Most of us love having our personal walk-in closet where we can keep all our expensive clothes, shoes and make-up essentials in an organised manner, but to have a walk-in closet in a minimal space is nothing less than a distant dream. We at Design Cafe are here to help you enjoy a clutter-free life while getting you 20% extra space. So here we have designed a walk-in closet in your bedroom that is separated by a glass wall. This will help you live your dreams without cramping up your bedroom. Use some intricate pendant lights and cove lights to set the correct ambience in your bedroom. You can go for a glass wall or a sliding door as a partition as per your convenience or need.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-5 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024141\/a-sliding-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-and-walk-in-closet.jpg\" alt=\"A sliding glass wall design for bedroom and walk-in closet\" data-id=\"26731\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024141\/a-sliding-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-and-walk-in-closet.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=26731\" class=\"wp-image-26731\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024141\/a-sliding-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-and-walk-in-closet.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024141\/a-sliding-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-and-walk-in-closet-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024141\/a-sliding-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-and-walk-in-closet-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024141\/a-sliding-glass-wall-design-for-bedroom-and-walk-in-closet-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Japanese Glass Partition Wall For Your Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This modern bedroom is separated from the living room through Japanese-style glass walls. The design is perfect if you want to bring in a lot of natural light to your room while creating subtle privacy in your bedroom. The wooden flooring complements the Japanese style glass wall beautifully, while the tall indoor plants and pendant lights add layers to this chic home interior. The design brings in a lot of positivity and lends a cosy vibe to the entire space.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-6 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024328\/japanese-master-bedroom-glass-wall-for-your-bedroom.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Japanese master bedroom glass wall for your bedroom lot of natural lights streaming into the space\" data-id=\"26732\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024328\/japanese-master-bedroom-glass-wall-for-your-bedroom.jpg.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=26732\" class=\"wp-image-26732\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024328\/japanese-master-bedroom-glass-wall-for-your-bedroom.jpg.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024328\/japanese-master-bedroom-glass-wall-for-your-bedroom.jpg-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024328\/japanese-master-bedroom-glass-wall-for-your-bedroom.jpg-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/25024328\/japanese-master-bedroom-glass-wall-for-your-bedroom.jpg-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you in love with these designs and super excited to own a glass wall bedroom? Book a free consultation with our designers today. They will help you with the best design suggestions that suit your requirement, preference and budget as well. And for more such exciting home interior design ideas, do check our blog and guides section.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want to know what kind of bedroom designs suits you\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02170353\/what-kind-of-bedroom-designs-suits-you.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you liked reading about glass wall bedroom designs, also have a look at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/glass-partition-for-living-room\/\">glass partition for living room<\/a>.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/ww